{"word":"autodenominarse","priority":"☆☆☆","meanings":[{"part_of_speech":"verb","transitivity":"pronominal","definition":"(人・集団が)自称する、自らを～と呼ぶ","english_definition":"(of a person or group) to call oneself; to refer to oneself as.","examples":[{"sentence":"El grupo se autodenomina 'Los revolucionarios'.","translation":"そのグループは自らを「革命家たち」と名乗っている。"},{"sentence":"Prefiere autodenominarse 'artista independiente'.","translation":"彼は自らを「インディペンデントアーティスト」と呼ぶことを好む。"}],"collocations":["autodenominarse como (～と自称する)","autodenominarse 'X' (「X」と自称する)"],"synonyms":["llamarse","designarse","titularse"],"antonyms":[]}],"etymology":{"value":"'auto-' (自己) + 'denominar' (命名する) + '-se' (再帰代名詞) から構成される。","priority":"★★☆"},"pronunciation":{"ipa":"/au̯.to.de.no.miˈnaɾ.se/","syllables":"au-to-de-no-mi-nar-se"},"inflection":{"verb_forms":{"present_simple":["me autodenomino","te autodenominas","se autodenomina","nos autodenominamos","os autodenomináis","se autodenominan"],"past_simple":["me autodenominé","te autodenominaste","se autodenominó","nos autodenominamos","os autodenominasteis","se autodenominaron"],"future_simple":["me autodenominaré","te autodenominarás","se autodenominará","nos autodenominaremos","os autodenominaréis","se autodenominarán"],"present_subjunctive":["me autodenomine","te autodenomines","se autodenomine","nos autodenominemos","os autodenominéis","se autodenominen"],"past_subjunctive":["me autodenominara/ase","te autodenominaras/ases","se autodenominara/ase","nos autodenomináramos/ásemos","os autodenominarais/aseis","se autodenominaran/asen"],"imperative":["autodenomínate (tú)","autodenomínese (usted)","autodenominémonos (nosotros/as)","autodenominaos (vosotros/as)","autodenomínense (ustedes)"],"gerund":"autodenominándose","participle":"autodenominado"}},"usage_notes":{"explanation":"「autodenominarse」は再帰動詞であり、主語自身が特定の名前や称号で呼ばれることを意味します。通常、ある個人またはグループが自分自身をどのように表現するかを説明するために使用されます。","priority":"★★★"},"common_mistakes":{"examples":[{"incorrect":"✗ El se autodenomina doctor.